.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
gtssmooth [OPTION] LAMBDA NITER < file.gts > smooth.gts
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
Smooth a GTS file by applying NITER iterations of a Laplacian filter
of parameter LAMBDA.
.SH OPTIONS
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.BI \-\-fold\fB= VAL, \ \-f \ VAL
Smooth only folds
.TP
.B \-\-verbose,  \-v
Print statistics about the surface.
.TP
.B \-\-help,  \-h
Display this help and exit.
